item.title: Driver dead after car hits tree
item.description: Police are investigating a fatal crash which claimed the life of male driver after his car left the road and struck a tree in Victoria’s central highlands this morning.

item.title: Young boy dies in Melbourne house fire
item.description: A child has died after fire engulfed a public housing block in Fitzroy North, Melbourne, on Saturday.

item.title: Police probe Brisbane businessman’s ‘suspicious’ death
item.description: A major investigation is underway following the shock discovery of a Brisbane businessman’s body in a Cairns apartment.

item.title: Protesters defy court order
item.description: Six people have been arrested after protesters took to one of Brisbane’s busiest thoroughfares in defiance of a Brisbane Supreme Court order that banned the march.

item.title: Woman critical and Qld highway shut
item.description: A woman is fighting for life after a two-car crash northwest of Brisbane that has also closed a major roadway.

item.title: Surfer punches shark in NSW attack
item.description: A quick-thinking surfer punched a shark until it let go of his surfing companion while catching waves on the NSW mid-north coast.

item.title: Victorian COVID-19 death toll drops
item.description: Victoria has recorded another 303 new cases of coronavirus and one of its lowest death tolls in weeks as stage 4 restrictions start to reduce the impact of the state’s second wave.

item.title: Qld records two-week virus streak
item.description: Queensland has recorded its 14th consecutive day without any COVID-19 community transmission, as Premier Annastacia Palaszczuk confirmed there had been no new cases in the 24 hours to Saturday.

item.title: ‘Last of a great generation’ honoured
item.description: The “last of a great generation” and Australians across the country have paid their respects on the 75th anniversary of the end of World War II.

item.title: Victorians get Grand Final reward
item.description: Victorians will still get a public holiday on the Friday before the AFL Grand Final even if it is not played in Melbourne.
